title: Plant-Based Mushroom Ravioli & Capsicum Sauce with Herby Pangrattato & Cucumber Salad
description: We love ravioli for all the flavours you can put together in one dish—from the inside out. Tonight’s meal is no exception: Ravioli
stuffed with mushrooms are the base for a tonne of other great flavours: a bursting tomato sauce, sweet sautéed capsicum and a herby pangrattato. Together, it’s a plant-based meal you’ll be sure to rave(ioli) about to your friends.

